title: Hero MotoCorp launches Euro-5 compliant variants in Turkiye
description: The company's product range in Turkiye, where it is present since 2014, includes the Xpulse 200 motorcycle, Dash 110 and Dash 125 scooters, which are sold through a network of over 100 touchpoints.
